{"type":"message","id":"7e9493fb","parentId":"0507b658","timestamp":"2026-03-18T07:22:48.428Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"好的，模板也创建成功了。现在让我创建一个案例：","thinkingSignature":"20254b989612d7c3f979ff2c81c6459c68c4eaa72c28195865a459eddd913130"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_ivfqan54s77y_1","name":"write","arguments":{"content":"# 飞书多维表格批量创建案例\n\n> 实战：从单条操作到批量操作的优化\n\n---\n\n## 背景\n\n需要创建 50 条任务记录到飞书多维表格。\n\n---\n\n## 踩坑过程\n\n### 第一次：单条创建（失败）\n\n```python\n# 错误的做法：循环单条创建\nfor task in tasks:\n    feishu_bitable_app_table_record create(\n        app_token=\"xxx\",\n        table_id=\"xxx\",\n        fields={\"任务名\": task}\n    )\n```\n\n**问题：**\n- 效率极低\n- API 调用次数过多\n- 耗时 5 分钟\n\n### 第二次：批量创建（成功）\n\n```python\n# 正确的做法：批量创建\nrecords = [\n    {\"fields\": {\"任务名\": task1}},\n    {\"fields\": {\"任务名\": task2}},\n    # ...\n]\n\nfeishu_bitable_app_table_record batch_create(\n    app_token=\"xxx\",\n    table_id=\"xxx\",\n    records=records\n)\n```\n\n**结果：**\n- 1 次 API 调用\n- 耗时 3 秒\n\n---\n\n## 经验总结\n\n| 操作 | 数量限制 | 推荐场景 |\n|------|----------|----------|\n| create | 单条 | 1-5 条 |\n| batch_create | 最多 500 条 | 5+ 条 |\n\n---\n\n## 核心教训\n\n> 批量操作优先于循环单条操作\n\n---\n\n*经验沉淀：每次踩坑都是进化机会*\n","file_path":"C:\\Users\\16343\\.openclaw\\agents\\guan-guan\\workspace\\knowledge\\case\\飞书批量操作优化案例.md"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":9179,"output":385,"cacheRead":36145,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":45709,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773818549099}}
